name: Theatrhythm: Final Bar Line - Digital Deluxe Edition
summary: This edition includes the 385 tracks in the Theatrhythm Final Bar Line core game and adds 27 “special music tracks” plus the 30 tracks from popular Square Enix games included in Season Pass 1 for a stunning 442 tracks to enjoy.
